com.ericbarnhill.jvcl

Class FTCPU

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ericbarnhill.jvcl.FTCPU

  • public class FTCPU
extends java.lang.Object
    This class performs Fourier-domain convolutions on the CPU. Arrays must be rectangular i.e. non-ragged. Array and kernel must have the same dimension.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    ericbarnhill
